<p>You can use jQuery <code>is()</code> function to check the selected element visible or hidden. This method traverses along the DOM elements to find a match, which satisfies the passed parameter. It will return true if there is a match otherwise returns false.</p>

<pre><code>&lt;script&gt;
    ($("#myelement").is(":visible"))? alert("#myelement is visible") : alert("#myelement is hidden");
&lt;/script&gt;
</code></pre>
